    "4 Econometrics We use a dierences-in-dierences design to estimate the causal eect of Manne attendance relative to colleague judges who have not yet attended the Manne program.",
    "This section provides information on the internal validity of the research design.",
    "Additional information is reported in Appendix C.",
    "20 The data contain information on prison sentences, probation sentences, nes, and the death penalty.",
    "We do not consider the death penalty, as it is rare in federal courts (just 71 cases)."
